author: Fearless & Far
description:
Liberia is one of those places that instantly grabs your attention — old colonial buildings crumbling by the ocean, streets full of history, and a slower pace that makes you pay attention. In this video, we walk through what’s left behind, hear stories from locals, and take in the atmosphere of a town that’s seen a lot. Then we make our way to meet the Grebo people, learning about their traditions, their identity, and the warrior history that still shapes their community today.
